re and agri-food occupations<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>You must also meet all the eligibility requirements for one of the three economic immigration programs: the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/federal-skilled-worker-program\/\"><strong>Federal Skilled Worker Program<\/strong><\/a>, the\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/canadian-experience-class\/\">Canadian Experience Class<\/a><\/strong>, or the\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/federal-skilled-trades-program\/\">Federal Skilled Trades Program<\/a><\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>As per the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/news\/canada-immigration-levels-plan-2023-2025\/\"><strong>Immigration Levels Plan 2023-2025<\/strong><\/a>, Canada aims to admit up to <strong>82,880<\/strong> newcomers through the Express Entry system by the end of 2023. This target is projected to increase to as high as <strong>114,000<\/strong> by the end of 2025. The implementation of category-based selection can help Canada achieve these targets while simultaneously addressing critical skills and labor shortages in the country&#8217;s workforce.<\/p>\n<p>https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/blog\/targeted-express-entry-for-engineers\/[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n<h2>Need Help with Category-Based Targeted Express Entry?<\/h2>\n<p>If you are a healthcare worker, STEM professional, or French language speaker wishing to start a life in Canada, now is the perfect time to take action. Our team is here to provide expert guidance and support, helping you turn your dreams of living and working in Canada into a reality.<\/p>\n<p>Meet <strong>Mr. Keshav Sharma<\/strong>, a highly qualified Regulated Canadian Immigration Consultant (RCIC) specializing in all types of Canadian immigration matters.<\/p>\n<p>For a limited time, eligible French-speaking candidates can take advantage of our comprehensive services starting at just CAD $999. Here&#8217;s what our tailored package includes: